    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Doton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 1 (Spell Level 1)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 2</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 13 | <b>Successes:</b> 1</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 1 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 12</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, F, S</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You cover yourself with a thin layer of earth, which provides you with a +1 natural armor bonus to Defense and a +1 deflection bonus to Defense against the next melee or ranged attack aimed at you. The shield weighs 1 lb per size category for creatures of Medium size or smaller (5 lbs for Medium creatures). For Large creatures, the shield weighs 10 lbs, and larger creatures increase that weight by 10 lbs per additional size category.</p>\n\n\n\n",
